# <type>(<scope>): <short summary> (max 72 chars)
#
# Types:
#   feat     — new feature or intent
#   fix      — bug fix
#   docs     — documentation only
#   refactor — code restructure, no behaviour change
#   chore    — deps, config, CI, gitignore, scripts
#   test     — tests only
#   perf     — performance improvement
#
# Scopes (optional):
#   whatsapp, db, account, owner, tenant, lead, gatekeeper,
#   intent, api, n8n, deploy, auth, models, seed, migration
#
# Body (optional — explain WHY, not WHAT):
#
# Examples:
#   feat(account): add QUERY_REFUNDS intent to AccountWorker
#   fix(gatekeeper): route key_user QUERY_DUES to AccountWorker
#   docs: update README to remove Twilio references
#   chore: add .env.template and .gitignore for xlsx files
#   refactor(owner): extract _shared helpers into _shared.py
